// [CR#704.5f]: a creature with toughness 0 or less is put into its owner's
// graveyard. A `Move` (not a destroy) — regeneration and indestructible cannot
// replace this; Leyline-style graveyard replacements still can. `scope` binds
// `This` to each creature; `when` reads its toughness.
[
    SbaRule(
        scope: Type(Creature),
        when: Compare(StatOf(This, Toughness), AtMost, 0),
        then: Move(This, Graveyard),
    ),
]
